'''Morcur Valley''' was a valley on [[Garos IV]] found to the east of [[Garan]].<ref name="WD">{{JournalCite|2|Whispers in the Dark}}</ref> The main [[Sundar]] settlement was in the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Northlan]] in the Upper Morcur Valley.<ref name="TP">{{JournalCite|5|Turning Point (Charlene Newcomb)}}</ref>

